50|$|Each DMO and LMO issues weather {{forecasts}} and warnings or advisories to {{the general}} public live in its own area. Weather data used to these forecasts are acquired from the Surface Observation (represented by the AMeDAS), the Radar Observation, the Upper-air <b>Observation</b> and the <b>Satellite</b> <b>Observation</b> mainly using the Himawari series.|$|R
